---
title: Caribbean Honey Chicken with Corn-Cauli Rice & Mayo
description: Enjoy a flavour-packed, guilt-free and nutritious meal with our brand-new cauliflower rice! With colourful
veggies stirred in and topped with our classic Caribbean-spiced chicken, we know you'll be glad you took the
plunge and gave this low carb delight a go.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
